The paper proposes a method for automatically answering questions about images by combining natural language processing and computer vision. This suggests that the paper could belong to multiple sub-categories in computer science, including natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and information retrieval (cs.IR). Among these, cs.CL and cs.CV are the most likely sub-categories as they are directly related to the paper's main focus.
